summary: Completed comprehensive frontend testing of Fynny Financial Wellbeing Dashboard. All major features tested successfully including navigation, lessons, microlearning, learning paths, and mobile responsiveness.
passed_tests: Main dashboard home screen loads correctly with sidebar, week tracker, and today's plan cards
Sidebar navigation works - all menu items navigate to correct screens
Learn with Fynny card expands when clicked to show lesson timeline
Microlearning cards (Daily Boost, Literacy Check, Money Tip) navigate to their respective screens
Lesson screens work with pagination (page indicators and CTA buttons)
Learning Path screen shows 4 themed journeys with progress indicators
Weekly commitment flow allows selecting an option and saving
Payment Plan, Calculators, Saved Lessons screens load correctly
Back navigation works from all screens
Mobile responsive - top bar shows on smaller screens and sidebar works correctly
